      "modified": "2026-04-13T00:00:00.000Z",
      "name": "Trivy/TeamPCP Supply Chain Attack",
      "description": "Multi-stage supply chain compromise targeting Trivy vulnerability scanner. Stage 1: malicious binary (v0.69.4). Stage 2: GitHub Actions tag manipulation (75/76 trivy-action tags). Stage 3: npm ecosystem expansion via stolen tokens (CanisterWorm). Credential theft at scale targeting CI/CD pipelines.",
      "first_seen": "2026-03-19T17:43:37Z",
      "last_seen": "2026-03-23T00:00:00Z"
    },
